Title: Batalin-Vilkovisky Formalism and Integration Theory on Manifolds

Authors: O.M. Khudaverdian and A. Nersessian

Comments: 15 pages, plain TeX, no figures

small corrections made in the formulae and two refs. addedJournal-ref: J.Math.Phys. 37 (1996) 3713-3724

The correspondence between the BV-formalism and integration theory onsupermanifolds is established. An explicit formula for the density on aLagrangian surface in a superspace provided with an odd symplectic structureand a volume form is proposed.